Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んっ んで 今日の\N宝の山の戦果はどうだったんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:24.04,Keiichi,Keiichi,0,0,0,,So, how'd things go with the treasure pile today?
